Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cho tôi nhìn thêm...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...những gương mặt đáng yêu đó nữa cơ
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Đủ rồi...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy vẫn còn yếu lắm.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Đến đây thôi
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.43,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cùng rời khỏi đây nào
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.37,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ừm.. vâng
